Now back to the grind!!!

I recently uploaded an EDC video on my YouTube of a few guns I carry and a few that I could carry, but don’t because it doesn’t suit me. I wanted to share it on IG, but it’s chopped down to 1 min. So go check out the full video if you’d like 🥰
#edc
.
@tier1concealed glock43 holster
